title: BIT.TRIP Complete Original Soundtrack
description:
BIT.TRIP is a series of rythm-based retro styled indie games from Gaijin Games. This torrent includes the official soundtrack for each game in the series (BEAT, CORE, VOID, RUNNER, FATE, and FLUX) in 230 kpbs MP3.
